    "reviews": [
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-12",
        "text": "Kara is an incredible photographer and person! I had been wanting to do a boudoir photo session for myself for awhile and after researching it, Kara seemed like the perfect fit and she was! I reached out to her to let her know why I was doing this (to honor my body for the journey it had been going through). Kara was kind and respectful about where I was at and what my needs were. She was professional and fun during the experience and made me feel incredibly comfortable with the whole experience. I wanted to do it outside and she found the perfect spots for it! Throughout the process before, during, and after she was such a joy to work with. I highly recommend Boho Chic Boudoir and Kara as a photographer!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-05",
        "text": "I have gotten to work with Kara three times now and every time, she exceeds my amazement a million times over! But our Boho Chic Boudoir was one of my favorites! I was really nervous which was one of the reasons I loved having two friends there with me. Not only did we get to do a lot of cool shots together, but it also allowed for time to get comfortable and share different ideas. But the biggest thing that made this day so special is the confidence that grew throughout the entire day. Kara makes your time about having fun and finding all the ways to help a woman feel powerful, confident, and reach her fullest beauty. Women are amazing and deserve to be shown as such. Having two friends share in the experience of such an empowering day was priceless. Kara will be our family photographer forever and I would recommend her to everyone I know!! Thank for an amazing experience, Kara!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-04",
        "text": "Kara is so fun to work with! I was so excited to try a boudoir session but definitely nervous since I’ve never had professional photos taken but Kara made it so easy and fun! She showed me how to pose and where to look which I was so appreciative of, and the photos turned out amazing, I am so impressed with her work.\n10/10 recommend 😄"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-07",
        "text": "Kara is an amazing photographer with people skills that make her subjects extremely comfortable. I was nervous for a boudoir photo shoot, but by the end, we were both laughing through silly poses with amazing results. She has also photographed friend’s weddings and is able to blend into the scene flawlessly while getting crucial shots you WILL want. 100% recommend for any style photo shoots."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-05",
        "text": "Kara made this one of the most amazing experiences of my life. Not only is she fun and made me fall back in love with my body, but she took the BEST photos of me I have ever seen. She is kind, talented, competitively priced, and a master behind the lense. I would recommend her to any one and everyone!"
      }
    ]
